ify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 flex-1 min-w-0\"><a aria-label=\"Home\" class=\"shrink-0 inline-block\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Jomnus\" width=\"100\" height=\"32\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-20 sm:w-24 md:w-28 lg:w-32 object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent;height:auto\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></a><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors bg-blue-50/80 text-blue-600\" href=\"/aboutUs\">About Us</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/contactUs\">Contact Us</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3\"><a href=\"/auth/signin\" class=\"px-4 lg:px-5 py-2 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors\">Log In</a><a href=\"/auth/register\" class=\"px-4 lg:px-5 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors shadow-sm\">Sign Up</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"md:hidden p-2 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-lg transition text-slate-600\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav></header><main><div class=\"w-full\"><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-14 md:py-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><span class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs uppercase tracking-wider\">Our Mission</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-6 leading-tight text-slate-900\">Connecting <br/>Peoples to help people.</h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-slate-500 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg\">We created this platform to connect people who need help with trusted local experts. It&#x27;s about building a community where individuals can support each other, share their skills, and earn money doing what they love.</p></div><div class=\"relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[40px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-500\"><img src=\"/images/teams/team.png\" alt=\"Team collaboration\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-cover aspect-4/3\"/></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-slate-50 py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-slate-900\">Born from a simple <br/>need: <span class=\"text-blue-600\">connection</span> <br/>and <span class=\"text-orange-500\">trust</span>.</h2><div class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><p>Our platform was created after recognizing that many people have skills and want to help, while others have tasks and lack the time or expertise to complete them.</p><p>We wanted a community where people can support each other. ជំនួស (JOMNUS) was born out of a desire to create a trusted space where collaboration strengthens both individuals and the community.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Values that Drive Us</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto mt-4 rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-orange-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Trust &amp; Safety</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Security is our top priority. We verify identities to ensure a safe environment.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users text-orange-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Community Growth</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">We foster a culture of mutual support and shared success.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star text-orange-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Professional Excellence</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">High standards in every task delivered within our marketplace.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye text-orange-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Radical Transparency</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Clear communication and honest feedback build lasting trust.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-blue-600 py-14 sm:py-16 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-orange-300/15 -translate-y-1/2\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-40 h-40 rounded-full bg-orange-300/15 -mr-12 -mt-12\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 sm:gap-12 text-center text-white\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div><div class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mb-2\">1k+</div><div class=\"text-blue-100 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Tasks Completed</div></div><div><div class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mb-2\">100</div><div class=\"text-blue-100 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Expert Performers</div></div><div><div class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mb-2\">24/7</div><div class=\"text-blue-100 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Customer Support</div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-blue-50/30\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900\">The Visionaries</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 mt-2\">Meet the team dedicated to making this vision a reality.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"bg-[#FDF2E9] w-full aspect-square rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:-translate-y-1\"><img src=\"/images/teams/raby.png\" alt=\"RABY\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\">RABY</h4><p class=\"text-blue-600 text-[11px] font-bold\">CEO</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"bg-[#FDF2E9] w-full aspect-square rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:-translate-y-1\"><img src=\"/images/teams/seyha.png\" alt=\"SEYHA\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\">SEYHA</h4><p class=\"text-blue-600 text-[11px] font-bold\">CTO</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"bg-[#FDF2E9] w-full aspect-square rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:-translate-y-1\"><img src=\"/images/teams/sreypi.png\" alt=\"SREYPI\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\">SREYPI</h4><p class=\"text-blue-600 text-[11px] font-bold\">CDO</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"bg-[#FDF2E9] w-full aspect-square rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden transition-all group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:-translate-y-1\"><img src=\"/images/teams/kanha.png\" alt=\"KANHA\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\">KANHA</h4><p class=\"text-blue-600 text-[11px] font-bold\">CIO</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"bg-[#FDF2E9] w-full aspect-square rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center justify-center